FBIS4-45545 "jptdd028__l94045" JPRS-TDD-94-028-L JPRS Narcotics 17 June 1994 LATIN AMERICA MEXICO Program for `All-Out Attack' on Drug Trafficking in Program for `All-Out Attack' on Drug Trafficking in Guadalajara Approved PA2106023394 Mexico City XEW Television Network in Spanish 0430 GMT 17 Jun 94 PA2106023394 Mexico City XEW Television Network Spanish BFN [From the "24 Hours" newscast] [Text] The Government of Jalisco State today approved the creation of a public security program for Guadalajara. Some 8,000 policemen will wage an all-out attack on narcotrafficking bands.
